1989;;After Midnight;;American;;Jim Wheat, Ken Wheat;;Marg Helgenberger, Marc McClure;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/After_Midnight_(1989_film);;Allison and Cheryl are two college students in a new class, The Psychology of Fear. It is taught by a strange man named Edward Derek. One of Derek's in class experiments makes a jock wet himself in front of everyone, leading to the censuring of the class. Professor Derek invites his students to his home for a private lesson. There, he tells the students three tales centered on fear. In the meantime, the humiliated jock sneaks over to Derek's home to take revenge.